column15:
The Federal Statistical Office collects the data on a number of health-releated issues. This includes 
the per-case statistics of hospital patients (1) in XLS and PDF format (2012, released in December 2013); 
operations and procedures in hospitals (2) in XLS and PDF format (2012, released in October 2013); 
costs of hospitals (3) (2012, released in December 2013); 
diagnostic data on hospital patients (4)in XLS and PDF format (2012, released in December 2013); 
detailed diagnostic data (4 digit ICD-10 codes) on hospital patients (5) in XLS format (2012, released in December 2013); 
detailed health expenses (6) in XLS and PDF format (2012, released in April 2014);

